    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood that has undergone a process that uses vacuum and pressure to force chemical preservatives into the wood. The goal of process is to protect the wood from termites or other insects and fungal decay; the wood has been found to contribute to environmental pollution.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
